novel "Lujin's Defense" ("La Course du Fou") which I have just received from Paris. The French edition is out of print, so I would like this copy back after you have read it.

I read with great interest what you had to say about the Anchor Review issue. It sounds wonderful.





Sincerely

Vladimir Nabokov





TO: MAURICE GIRODIAS

